          "text": "True statement(s) regarding feeding of HIV-infected child is/are –a)  Breast feeding for 4–6 months then start weaningb)  Breast feeding for 1 year then start weaning c) Exclusively top feedingd) Breast feeding for 6 months & then rapid weaning",
