          "explanation": "b. Hemolytic uremic syndrome(Ref: Nelson's 20/e p 2508, Ghai 8/e p 492)Neurologic findings (due to microthrombi formed in vessels of CNS) are present in TTP in addition to the triad seen in HUS (Microangiopathic hemolytic anemia, Thrombocytopenia and Renal failure).",
