          "id": "medmcqa-6da303e1-467d-460a-8b4c-1ab3b6419d0e",
          "text": "Kallu 2 yrs child weighing 6.7 Kg presents in the casualty with history of vomiting & diarrohea for last 2 days. On examination skin pinch over the ant. abdominal wall go quickly to its original position. Interpretation of skin - pinch test in this child will be-",
