          "id": "medmcqa-3a790e91-6887-40a1-a3c2-90faeb17e734",
          "text": "An 8 days old neonate presents with hypoglycemia (Glucose - 17 mg%) and jaundice is diagnosed to have metabolic disorder. Most likely diagnosis:",
