          "id": "medmcqa-6eae2501-acb2-493c-b310-8c1c38cbadf9",
          "text": "Which of the following agents is likely to cause cerebral calcification and hydrocephalus in a newborn whose mother has history of taking spiramycin but was not complaint with therapy ?",
